my cat is poorly he has been unusually quiet for the past week or more he doesnt greet me when i come home or jump up on my lap anymore he has done this everyday since we got him as a kitten he isnt playing with his brother either just sleeping all day hardly moving when he does walk he has his back arched and is taking small steps walking very slowly like his leg back is hurting or something any ideas until we can get him to the vets on monday hi i would call your local vet asap he probably hurt himself jumping off something and may have broken a hip i would also place him on several baby blankets they are extra soft and warm and place a heating pad under those blanket turned on low put his food and water dish next to the blanket area and let him have total privacy turn on a night lite in the room and soft music turned on low or a waterfall sound if you have one he will need alot of time and comfort to heal properly good luck and i do hope your kitty is feeling better soon Atomic Kitten Equine conformation Aerial (dance move) Mattress Swingout Cat Kitchen Professional wrestling double-team maneuvers Professional wrestling holds Guinea pig 1957 World Series Customs and etiquette of Japan Friends The Time Machine Poker jargon Figure skating Jon Secada Piccolo Junior Saga Ferret Weight training Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Upholstery Japanese tea ceremony Van Halen Glossary of ballet terms Shaggy dog story Kitten Soap opera Eddie Guerrero Big Brother UK series 6 Cliff Richard Strap-on dildo Sleep Professional wrestling attacks Blankets (graphic novel) Social rule Sin City What Ever Happened to Baby Jane? (film) Casualty lifting Socialization Tofu Castlevania: Symphony of the Night The Dalek Invasion of Earth Little Britain Milton H. Erickson Chair Breaststroke Dishwasher Russian joke Futurama (TV series - season 5) Tlingit Pakistani cricket team in West Indies in 2005 Wound Sauna Wild at Heart (Buffy episode) Hiking The Amber Spyglass Conker's Bad Fur Day Characters in